Discord Bot Terms of Use [TBS]

Welcome to using the "[TBS]" Discord bot. Your access to and use of the bot is subject to these Terms of Service. By using the bot, you agree to comply with and be bound by these terms. If you do not agree to any of these terms, please do not use our bot.

Responsible Behavior:

You must use the bot responsibly and comply with local laws and Discord community regulations.
User Content:

If you provide content via the bot, you grant the bot operator the right to use, modify, publish and distribute such content for the purpose of providing the service.
Confidentiality:

We respect your privacy. Please see our Privacy Policy for more details on the collection and use of your personal data.
Changes to the Terms:

We reserve the right to change these Terms of Service at any time. We recommend that you review these terms regularly to be aware of any changes.

Through giveaways, when you enter, the bot will automatically save your discord id in a database and then announce the winner of the giveaway, the saved data will be deleted via a bot command and/or via auto-delete


